Package: nbconv
Title: Evaluate the sum of arbitrary negative binomial distributions.
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Gregory", "Bedwell", , "gregoryjbedwell@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0456-0032"))
Maintainer: Greg Bedwell <gregoryjbedwell@gmail.com>
Depends: R (>= 4.2), parallel, matrixStats     
Description: nbconv implements three different methods for evaluating the sum of negative binomial distributions with arbitrary parameters. The three methods are: Furman's exact PMF, a saddlepoint approximation, and a method of moments approximation.
License: use_gpl3_license()
Encoding: UTF-8
